      <li style="padding:0.5rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #1A3A1A;"><a href="/how-much-does-a-cmo-cost" style="color:#00C853;text-decoration:none;">How much does a (full-time) CMO cost? →</a></li>
      <li style="padding:0.5rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #1A3A1A;"><a href="/when-to-hire-your-first-cmo" style="color:#00C853;text-decoration:none;">When to hire your first CMO →</a></li>
      <li style="padding:0.5rem 0;"><a href="/fractional-cmo", style="color:#00C853;text-decoration:none;">Treetop\'s Fractional CMO service →</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="sec-inner">
    <div class="cta-box">
      <div>
        <div class="cta-text">Considering a fractional engagement?</div>
        <div class="cta-sub">Take the 3-minute Gap Assessment first — it tells you whether fractional CMO is actually the right fix for your specific gaps.</div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <a href="/quiz" class="btn-p">Take the Gap Assessment →</a>
        <a href="/fractional-cmo" class="btn-g">See Fractional CMO service</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

